title: Ville-Valtteri Starck
text: Ville-Valtteri Starck (born 3 February 1995) is a <a href="Finland">Finnish</a> <a href="Association%20footballer">footballer</a> who currently plays for <a href="FC%20Jazz">FC Jazz</a> in the Finnish second tier <a href="Ykk%C3%B6nen">Ykkönen</a>. He has previously played three seasons in the Finnish top division <a href="Veikkausliiga">Veikkausliiga</a> for <a href="Turun%20Palloseura">TPS Turku</a>.
